Hi everyone. I just got a psp go and am trying to put some games on it but i keep getting "files corrupted" when i transferr it to the psp. I have power iso but haven't really used it except to mount games on my pc. Any advice would be really appreciated, thanks.
As far as i know there is no way to play ISO-images on PSP Go! at the moment. The only way for you to play games is to buy 'em on UMD's or to download 'em via PS Store (for a fee ofcourse).
